trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for selecting a URL.
trans-unit.target: Gir et brukergrensesnitt for å velge en URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: UrlEditor is a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor> that provides a dialog box for selecting a URL.
trans-unit.target: UrlEditor er en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor>som gir en dialogboks for å velge en URL-adresse.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the caption to display on the selection dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Henter teksten skal vises i dialogboksen for valg.

trans-unit.source: The caption to display on the selection dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Teksten som skal vises i dialogboksen for valg.

trans-unit.source: Edits the value of the specified object using the editor style provided by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor.GetEditStyle*> method.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer verdien for det angitte objektet ved hjelp av redigeringsprogrammet-stil fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor.GetEditStyle*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor.GetEditStyle*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> object that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> objekt som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: A service provider object through which editing services may be obtained.
trans-unit.target: En leverandør Webtjenesteobjektet som redigering services kan hentes.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the value being edited.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av verdien som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: The new value of the object.
trans-unit.target: Den nye verdien for objektet.

trans-unit.source: If the value of the object hasn't changed, this method should return the same object it was passed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for objektet ikke er endret, må denne metoden returnere det samme objektet det ble sendt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the file name filter string for the editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter filen navnet Filterstrengen for redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: This is used to determine the items that appear in the file list of the dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Dette brukes til å fastslå hvilke elementer som vises i listen over filer i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains information about the file filtering options available in the dialog box.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder informasjon om filen filtrering alternativene i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor.EditValue*> method.
trans-unit.target: Henter redigering stilen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor.EditValue*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UrlEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> object that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> objekt som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> values indicating the provided editing style.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref> verdier som angir det angitte redigering stil.

trans-unit.source: If the method is not supported, this method will return <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ikke støttes hvis, denne metoden tilbakestiller <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the options for the URL builder to use.
trans-unit.target: Henter alternativene for URL-verktøyet til å bruke.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.UrlBuilderOptions"></xref> that indicates the options for the URL builder to use.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.UrlBuilderOptions"> </xref> som angir alternativene for URL-verktøyet til å bruke.
